name: Crossy Doge
description:
Young Doge The Third has lost his frisbee at the park, and needs help navigating much chaotic roads to get it back!

Climb the live in-game leaderboards to the moon and blast across 4 very wow, much impress environments from low earth orbit to Elon's mars hideout in this very EPIC quest.

The leaderboards will stay live after the gamejam.

I much appreciate any tips, It's been a blast to make!

DOGE WALLET: D7yGgnbqyX7hS9nSnffp2ArAmJCMSTXTgm
